summary: adds mannnequins to breezehome, Hjerim, Proudspire Manor, and honeyside.
descriptionHtml:
this mod was made on request. 

this adds mannequins to 

Breezehome -- 2 Mannequins at the Alchemy Lab room against the Window Wall

Hjerim -- 1 mini mannequin to the left of the Hidden Room on a cabinet

hjerim -- go upstairs turn around and look in room with candles. between the canles

proudspire manor -- 2 by back door

Honeyside -- wall to the right of weapon rack.

feel free to add your own pics. 
In game i use the tester so he doesn\'t own full upgrade house.
author: Ryoskeith
